
** Install Perl

  see also GcpPerl

  - get latest perl from perl.org

$ ./conifgure.gnu
$ make
$ sudo make install


** Oracle

  https://github.com/perl5-dbi/DBD-Oracle

*Make sure http_proxy is set as root!!!*

$ sudo /usr/local/bin/perl -MCPAN -e "install DBI"
$ sudo /usr/local/bin/perl -MCPAN -e "install Switch"

  ORACLE_HOME: Database

$ sudo \
ORACLE_HOME=$ORACLE_HOME \
PATH=$ORACLE_HOME/bin:$PATH \
LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$ORACLE_HOME/lib \
/usr/local/bin/perl -MCPAN -e "install DBD::Oracle"

  ORACLE_HOME: Instant Client
  
$ sudo \
ORACLE_HOME=$ORACLE_HOME \
PATH=$ORACLE_HOME:$PATH \
LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$ORACLE_HOME \
/usr/local/bin/perl -MCPAN -e "install DBD::Oracle"

